author: Reuters Editorial
title: Peugeot restarts car production in virus-hit Wuhan with Dongfeng
description: French automaker Peugeot SA's joint venture in China with Dongfeng Motor Group <0489.HK> said on Wednesday it had restarted car production at its plant in Wuhan city, the epicenter of China's coronavirus outbreak.
content:
BEIJING (Reuters) - French automaker Peugeot SA’s (PEUP.PA) joint venture in China with Dongfeng Motor Group (0489.HK) said on Wednesday it had restarted car production at its plant in Wuhan city, the epicenter of China’s coronavirus outbreak.
